section.title: file documentation
section.DESCRIPTION:
This specification documents Major Version 1 of the Qualcomm technologies, Inc Messaging Interface (QMI) for WLAN cnss platform driver and daemon components.
CNSS plaform has two components: a kernel driver and user space daemon. These components interact for calibration and QDSS functionality. CNSS platform driver communicates the information from this exchanges to WLAN firmware.
